<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 03:15:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>上半年城镇新增就业698万人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-adds-698-mln-urban-new-jobs-first-half-year-2024-07-23/</link><description>据人力资源部称，中国周二表示，今年上半年城镇新增就业698万人。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 02:51:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-adds-698-mln-urban-new-jobs-first-half-year-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称中国调整贷款抵押品将缓解“资产荒”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinas-loan-collateral-tweak-will-ease-asset-famine-state-media-says-2024-07-23/</link><description>官方媒体周二援引消息人士的话说，中国央行决定降低中期贷款抵押要求，将缓解债券市场的“资产荒”压力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 02:25:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinas-loan-collateral-tweak-will-ease-asset-famine-state-media-says-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>尽管中美关系日益紧张，制药巨头仍将目光投向中国寻求交易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/drug-giants-eye-china-deals-despite-growing-sino-us-tensions-2024-07-23/</link><description>行业高管和投资银行家表示，一些全球最大的制药商并未因中美紧张局势加剧而望而却步，正在中国寻找交易，以补充药品管道并提高其在全球第二大制药市场的影响力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 02:17:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/drug-giants-eye-china-deals-despite-growing-sino-us-tensions-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>随着芯片股反弹，亚洲结束连跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-23/</link><description>亚洲股市周二从一个月低点反弹，台湾股市结束了五连跌，半导体股在华尔街复苏中领涨，而大宗商品价格下跌打压澳元。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 01:56:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>台风“高美”逼近台湾，台湾缩减年度军事演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-curtails-annual-war-games-typhoon-gaemi-barrels-towards-island-2024-07-23/</link><description>由于台风“盖美”猛冲台湾，预计将带来强风和暴雨，台湾周二缩减了一年一度的汉光战争演习。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 01:55:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-curtails-annual-war-games-typhoon-gaemi-barrels-towards-island-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>五角大楼表示，俄罗斯和中国在北极的合作不断加强</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/growing-cooperation-between-russia-china-arctic-pentagon-says-2024-07-23/</link><description>美国军方周一在发布北极地区战略时表示，俄罗斯和中国在北极地区的合作日益增多，这可能会影响地区稳定。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 01:44:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/growing-cooperation-between-russia-china-arctic-pentagon-says-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>澳元、新西兰元因中国降息而苦苦挣扎；美元漂流</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/aussie-kiwi-dollars-struggle-chinas-rate-cuts-dollar-adrift-2024-07-23/</link><description>在中国下调几项关键利率后，澳元和新西兰元周二徘徊在数周低点附近，而美元在等待新的推动力时几乎没有变化。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 01:01:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/aussie-kiwi-dollars-struggle-chinas-rate-cuts-dollar-adrift-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：随着拜登出局，股市反弹，选举局势混乱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-2024-07-22/</link><description>奥尔登·本特利 (Alden Bentley) 展望亚洲市场未来一天。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 21:50:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>伯克希尔哈撒韦公司将比亚迪股份减持至5%以下</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/berkshire-hathaway-cuts-stake-chinas-byd-below-5-2024-07-22/</link><description>沃伦·巴菲特的伯克希尔·哈撒韦公司将其在比亚迪的股份降至 5% 以下，这可能是伯克希尔哈撒韦公司最后一次披露中国最大电动汽车生产商的股票销售情况。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 14:04:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/berkshire-hathaway-cuts-stake-chinas-byd-below-5-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>油轮丑闻后，中国卡车和食品制造商试图重新赢得消费者信任</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-truck-food-makers-attempt-regain-consumer-trust-after-tanker-scandal-2024-07-22/</link><description>中国的卡车制造商周一发布了运载食用油的车辆的安全标准，在有关运输食用油的油罐车的报道重新引发人们对食品污染的担忧后，各公司试图重新获得消费者的信任。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 13:05:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-truck-food-makers-attempt-regain-consumer-trust-after-tanker-scandal-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>基辅称乌克兰最高外交官本周将访华谈和</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraines-top-diplomat-visit-china-this-week-talk-peace-kyiv-says-2024-07-22/</link><description>乌克兰最高外交官将于周二应北京邀请访问中国，并举行会谈，基辅称会谈重点是如何结束俄罗斯在乌克兰的战争，以及中国在达成解决方案方面可能发挥的作用。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 11:04:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraines-top-diplomat-visit-china-this-week-talk-peace-kyiv-says-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>总统称菲律宾“不能让步”其南海立场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-cannot-yield-its-south-china-sea-position-president-says-2024-07-22/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周一表示，菲律宾在南海的立场“不能让步”、“不能动摇”，但将找到缓解争议海域紧张局势的方法。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 09:27:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-cannot-yield-its-south-china-sea-position-president-says-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾表示在与中国达成补给协议后仍维护南海权利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-still-assert-south-china-sea-rights-after-resupply-deal-with-2024-07-22/</link><description>菲律宾外交部周一表示，在与中国就向有争议的仁爱礁执行补给任务达成“临时安排”后，菲律宾将继续维护其在南海的权利。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 07:52:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-still-assert-south-china-sea-rights-after-resupply-deal-with-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国允许延迟退休以应对人口问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-allow-delayed-retirement-combat-population-woes-2024-07-22/</link><description>中国将逐步提高法定退休年龄（目前是世界上最低的退休年龄之一），以允许人们工作更长时间，因为中国正在努力缓解养老金预算不断飙升的压力，许多省份已经面临赤字。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 07:51:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-allow-delayed-retirement-combat-population-woes-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国对其十年来的政策承诺的承诺面临越来越多的质疑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-faces-growing-scepticism-over-its-commitment-decade-old-policy-pledges-2024-07-22/</link><description>随着中国经济失衡加剧，北京方面面临的压力越来越大，要求兑现其在上周领导层议程制定会议上重申的长达十年之久的政策承诺，但近年来未能取得重大突破。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 07:06:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-faces-growing-scepticism-over-its-commitment-decade-old-policy-pledges-2024-07-22/</guid></item></channel></rss>